These are Puzzles for 1x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-1::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: scientific, horror, mystery, superhero, epic, zombie
1. the person watching horror movies is the person watching horror movies##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
3. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching epic movies##5
4. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the person watching zombie movies##8
5. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching zombie movies##2
8. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |      4       |   5    |   6   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | horror | zombie | superhero | scientific | mystery |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-2::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, tea, juice, lemonade, hot-chocolate, fanta
1. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
2. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
4. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
6. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
7. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
8. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |  3   |    4     |   5    |   6   |
| Beverage   | 7up | lemonade | tea | juice | hot-chocolate | fanta |

