.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-3::.
6 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, fish, pony, chinchilla, dog
1. the owner of the ferret is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
3. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
4. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
6. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |   3   |     4      |  5  |   6    |
| Pet   | pony | dog | fish | ferret | chinchilla | hamster |

