.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: golf, badminton, soccer, climbing, basketball, sailing
1. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
2. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##8
3. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person who's sport is golf##8
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |    3    |     4      |       5       |    6     |
| Sport   | soccer | badminton | climbing | basketball | sailing | golf |

