.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-5::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: tennis, skiing, swimming, rowing, water-polo, soccer
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##8
 3. the person who's sport is soccer is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##5
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is rowing##2
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is rowing##7
 8. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##5
 9. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##8
10. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |    4     |   5   |       6       |
| Sport   | soccer | tennis | swimming | skiing | rowing | water-polo |

